"Tetris.instructions" = "# Sirtet\n\nA Tetris-style game with a twist: pieces rise from the bottom instead of falling from the top.\n\n## How to play\n\n- **Swipe left or right** to move the active piece.\n- **Tap** to rotate the piece.\n- **Swipe up** to hard-snap the piece to the top of the stack.\n- A new piece appears at the bottom on every tick.\n\n## Clearing lines\n\n- Fill a complete horizontal row to clear it.\n- Clearing **multiple lines at once** scores extra. A four-line clear is the biggest reward.\n\n## Levels and speed\n\nThe game speeds up as your score grows. Higher levels scroll pieces faster.\n\n## Game over\n\nThe game ends when a new piece can no longer enter the play field.";
"Version %@ (%@)" = "Version %1$@ (%2$@)";
